{"tid":2177652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣館長凌晨遭槍擊！右手、右腳中彈　倒臥血泊緊急送醫","createTime":"2020-08-28T01:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T06:03:17.000Z","uid":322230,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"af1973b757e054f427a516b293afcaf52fda5580","tid":2177652,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T01:01:33.000Z","msg":"館長陳之漢28日凌晨2時許在林口館遭人連開3槍，右手與右大腿中彈倒地（中2槍），事發後他的員工也立刻在臉書直播，可以看見館長躺在地上神情痛苦，旁邊員工用力替他緊壓右腳與右手的傷口。警方目前已趕到現場處理，館長也已送醫治療中，詳細情況待進一步釐清。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，館長對著鏡頭不斷哀嚎，強忍疼痛說，若是他這次不幸死亡，希望網友可以傳承他的精神，並好好照顧他的家人。<br />\n記者致電成吉思汗健身房林口館，員工低調不願透露任何消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1795269&amp;from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1795269%26from%3Dfb_et_news&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=50e6d7e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php?news_id=1795269&amp;from=fb_et_news</a>"},{"pid":"e7668a45bbd830602979f83a9db87c83ae5a3ad6","tid":2177652,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T01:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9faa98d3179be1378c447f7753219446e77669","tid":2177652,"uid":91224,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"點解中槍都可以第一時間開直播...  好有喜感"},{"pid":"ab0dbafaa93636097196aaa685fc317b2ad1e6ca","tid":2177652,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"af9faa98d3179be1378c447f7753219446e77669","tid":2177652,"uid":91224,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T01:09:56.000Z","msg":"點解中槍都可以第一時間開直播...  好有喜感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"館長天大命大<br />\n唔使救都可以自然復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda128dac56bfb73800ce187b9adab6b3fc8e105","tid":2177652,"uid":321843,"like